Currently Sugar is lacking integration when compared with a standard Desktop Environment such as XFCE.

This project is about improving Sugar for running better alongside a regular Desktop.

Goals achieved (merged):

* Patch to show app icons in Frame
* Patch to run Sugar Activities outside Sugar

Patches sent:

* Run Sugar alongside traditional desktop

Goals to be completed:

* Standard startup notification
* Support for .desktop for launching applications
* Drag & Drop into home window
* Drag & Drop to/from Journal
* Expose Journal to filesystem
* Improve notification system